        "@id": "https://pinnacleblooms.org/therapy-materials/sensory-regulation/weighted-blanket-lap-pad#howto",
        "name": "How to Use a Weighted Blanket for Sensory Regulation",
        "description": "Complete step-by-step guide to safely and effectively use weighted blankets for children with autism, ADHD, and sensory processing needs.",
        "totalTime": "PT30M",
        "estimatedCost": {
